author: I_am_Groot
title: Keychain
review: Pretty good keychain overall. I'm surprised that we get a new face print instead of reusing the one from the Teen Groot figure that came in Thor's Weapon Quest. Sadly, of course you can not use the head on a normal figure unless you do some DIY work. Just like the normal figure, I wish it had leg printing. I'm not that in to keychains though, so I'm keeping mine sealed as of now.
